ntre sus calidades de construcción destacan la carpintería exterior de aluminio lacado en blanco, instalación completa de aire frío-calor, antena parabólica y de TV entre otras.There is a sunny communal swimming pool set in vast landscaped garden areas, with one basement parking space included in the price. Of note among the building specifications is the lacquered aluminium outdoor joinery in white, a complete hot-cold air conditioning system, communal satellite dish, among other features.';
