 coches, despacho, comedor y salón, además cada dormitorio posee su propio baño y terraza con impresionantes vistas al mar. 200 metros de terraza. La casa tiene aire acondicionado, calefacción central de agua, Domótica, la madera utilizada es toda de Iroco, carpintería metálica toda de Suco, con cristales de seguridad y puerta blindada. Se encuentra en una urbanización muy tranquila con guardia de seguridad.Luxury villa in La Veleta accompanied by a palm grove of more than 50 years old (about 45 palms) and swimming pool. The meters are built 800m2, has 4 bedrooms, 6 bathrooms, kitchen, laundry room. Separate pantry, garage with capacity for 2 cars, office, dining room and lounge, and each bedroom has its own bathroom and terrace with stunning sea views. 200 meters of terrace. The house has air conditioning, central water heating, Home Automation, the wood used is all of Iroko, all of Suco metalwork, safety glass and reinforced door. Located in a quiet urbanization with security guard.';
