al pools 6x3. Two 2 bedroom and 2 bathroom houses. Private access, оff road parking, сovered terrace, that can be glassed off in the future, views to salt lakes. Villa is located 5 minutes drive to the beach (town of Guardamar del Segura) and two minutes drive to the supermarkets, less tan two kilometers from the golf club La Marquesa. Each level is 2m lower so views are not blocked out by future developments of the area.';
