ada cerca de La Finca Golf Club, de diez minutos en coche del mar, y en cinco minutos del distrito comercial.Beautiful villa in a quiet urbanization of La Rellana. The house has three bedrooms and two bathrooms, a spacious sun deck and a terrace , and a parking place. Pre-installed air conditioning and alarm systems, reinforced insulation of walls, ceramic flooring inside and outside a non-slip surface, modern kitchen is only a part of the quality with which this villa was built. On a plot of 413 sqm there are a private swimming pool and a landscape garden. The villa is located close to La Finca Golf Club, a ten minute drive from the sea, and in five minutes from the commercial district.';
